Cucumber

BDD framework >> first we write feature and then we write the code

TDD >> Test Driven Development (first we write TC and then we write the code)

scenarios using gherkin language

gherkin is a simple plain english type language with few keywords


BDD is also known as GWT >> Given When Then

Given: pre conditions, what should already be present so that I start my actions
When: what actions user needs to perform
Then: what should be the result of those actions	